{
  "info": {
    "name": "POS Backend API",
    "description": "Point of Sale Backend System\n\n## Authentication\n- `POST /auth/login` is public.\n- `POST /auth/register` requires ADMIN token.\n- All other endpoints require `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header.\n- Token expires in 1 hour.\n\n## Role-Based Access\n| Role    | Permissions |\n|---------|-------------|\n| `admin` | Full access to everything |\n| `user`  | Read produk, create transactions, restock (stok-masuk), open/close shifts, reconciliation |\n\n## New Features\n- **Shift system**: Track kasir work shifts (open/close)\n- **Cash reconciliation**: At shift close, declare actual cash vs expected\n- **Void log**: Audit trail for deleted transactions\n- **Discount tracking**: Apply discounts with approval for >10%",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', jsonData.token);",
                  "    pm.test('Login success - token saved', () => {",
                  "        pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "        pm.expect(jsonData.token).to.not.be.empty;",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"050208\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login with credentials. Returns JWT token which is auto-saved to collection variable `token`. Default admin: admin / 050208"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register [ADMIN]",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"kasir3\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"role\": \"user\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Register a new user. REQUIRES ADMIN token. Role: 'admin' or 'user' (kasir)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "" },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "Logout. Client-side token discard (stateless JWT)."
          }
        }
      ],
      "description": "Authentication endpoints."
    },
